{"tid":657519,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《福爾摩斯 3》正式公布 2020年上映","createTime":"2018-05-08T07:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T11:49:39.000Z","uid":66943,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec390d60b46ef39b7cc69a4daaf1109c758747e","tid":657519,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:35:59.000Z","msg":"今天華納正式宣布了該系列的第三部，預定2020年12月25日聖誕檔期上映<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180508_cyl_36_1/gamersky_01small_02_201858877F0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180508_cyl_36_1%2Fgamersky_01small_02_201858877F0.jpg&h=a20e2d2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《福爾摩斯》前兩部由著名導演Guy Ritchie執導，雖然第三部是否繼續由其執導還不清楚，但華納已經決定了《Hannibal》的Chris Brancato譜寫第三部的劇本。<br />\n<br />\n《福爾摩斯》前兩部均為2009年和2011年的聖誕檔期上映，捲走了近11億美元的票房，後者與Tom Cruise大片《鬼影約章》的競爭中仍然瘋狂拿下了5.45億美元的票房令人驚嘆。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，《福爾摩斯》第三部的檔期將與James Cameron的《Avatar 2》直接對戰，《福爾摩斯》第一部就與《Avatar》對抗過，所以不必太過擔心票房，而迪士尼的一部未定名真人電影同樣將加入2020年聖誕檔期大戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://68.media.tumblr.com/06cc0f3404b4b99f65bb23ac0e722c1c/tumblr_otu5g5BgVc1r8fgv7o2_500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2F06cc0f3404b4b99f65bb23ac0e722c1c%2Ftumblr_otu5g5BgVc1r8fgv7o2_500.jpg&h=aa99dcb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ab7253ef732f36524b500c7962b8671953a8358","tid":657519,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/153714_407813ad245e06890e73445649cfe57d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F153714_407813ad245e06890e73445649cfe57d.gif&h=175675a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"199c48423ce94862e7da936298665891155dec3b","tid":657519,"uid":2189,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:18:15.000Z","msg":"Sherlock: Jarvis, who kill this m